Configure Segmentation Filters

Choose whether to use the model to get predictions on all data or on just a segment (subset) of the data. For example, you can focus on a specific product model or a group of customers.

If you want to add filters, select Yes, and specify one or more filters for each filter, select the field and operator, and then specify a value. Filter expressions are case-sensitive.

Click Next.
